= Red Guard Attack 

The Red Guards have staged attacks on banks across Italy, seemingly as a way to fund the organisation in its early stages. Though the Interior Ministry, in collaboration with the Carabinieri was able to prevent some of the attacks from succeeding, many were able to escape from the grasp of the Carabinieri.

[? if psi_in_government : Naturally, our party has come under flak for allowing this to occur, as opposition parties criticise our inability to stabilise the nation; some even going as far to paint the *Red Guards* act as affiliated to us. ?]

